github pages, and decided to make use of it and turn it into my blog. So here goes. ;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;bangkok&quot;&gt;Bangkok&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Background:&lt;/strong&gt; Sunyal, my friend from Mauritius back when I was still in university, was coming back to this region for a holiday. 
